feature::after.description: material after the end of the word

feature::appositioncontainer.description: 1 if it is an apposition container

feature::articular.description: 1 if the sentence, group, clause, phrase or wg has an article

feature::bookshort.description: book name (abbreviated) from ref attribute in xml

feature::chapter.description: chapter number, from ref attribute in xml

feature::discontinuous.description: 1 if the word is out of sequence in the xml

feature::nodeid.description: node id (as in the XML source data)

feature::num.description: generated number (not in xml): book: (Matthew=1, Mark=2, ..., Revelation=27); sentence: numbered per chapter; word: numbered per verse.

feature::trailer.description: material after the end of the word (excluding critical signs)

feature::trans.description: translation of the word surface text according to the Berean Interlinear Bible

feature::translit.description: transliteration of the word surface text

feature::typ.description: syntactical type (on sentence, group, clause or phrase)

feature::typems.description: morphological type (on word), syntactical type (on sentence, group, clause, phrase or wg)

feature::unaccent.description: word in unicode characters without accents and diacritical markers

feature::unicode.description: word in unicode characters plus material after it

feature::verse.description: verse number, from ref attribute in xml

freq: he, she, it, himself, herself, itself; even, very; same
